CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 25, 1957, pg. A17 reads: " "King And Queen"... for 1957 are there delightful young people. Miss Alice Jean Weatherly is the "queen" and William Hampton is the "king."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of 1956 "Queen" Valerie Johnson and "King" Wilmer Rogers, walking down stairs in Pittsburgh Room of the Penn Sheraton Hotel for the Alpha Kappa Alpha 1957 Cotillion
